{
  "id": "adv_main_02_09_03",
  "title": "東京編2章18話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_unrest-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "初戦がリズノワか～\nこれまた、波乱の幕開けやな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ we’re up against LizNoir first‚ huh?\nWhat a wild start.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。でも、遅かれ早かれこうなっていたわ\n私達がやるべきことは、変わらない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "True. But it would’ve happened sooner or later.\nIt doesn’t change anything for us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "全力で、勝ちにいく\nたとえ、恩のある星見プロが相手だろうと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ll do whatever we can to win‚\neven if we’re up against the people we’re indebted to.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.2666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.0333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.033333333333335
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "（優とすみれは、覚悟を持ってついて来てくれた）\n（それに報いるためにも、私達は三人でトップになるの）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Yu and Sumire resolved themselves to follow me here.)\n(To repay them‚ the three of us have to reach the top.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.466666666666665
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "（私達に残されたものは）\n（もう、それしかないのだから）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Besides‚ that’s all)\n(we have left for us.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.9666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、全力で戦うんが星見プロへの礼儀というか\nケジメみたいなもんやからなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "True‚ fighting with everything we’ve got is our way\nof paying respect and settling things with them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、うちはちゃんと覚悟出来てます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m ready for it‚ of course.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 47.26666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "私も、覚悟出来てるよ！\nそれに、ちょっと思い出したことがあるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m ready as well!\nBesides‚ I just remembered something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "前に、朝倉さんに言われたこと……覚えてる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you remember… what Mr. Asakura once told us?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "昨日のライブを見て、改めて思ったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I realized something seeing your concert yesterday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "トリエルとリズノワが同じステージに立った時",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When TRINITYAiLE and LizNoir stand on the same stage‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "その化学反応は、新たな時代を生むビッグバンになると",
      "translations": {
        "en": "the chemical reaction will cause a big bang that will birth a new era.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんよ\nどんな経緯であれ、やっとその機会に巡り会えた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course.\nWhatever the case‚ we finally have an opportunity.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "存分に楽しむためにも、しっかり仕上げていきましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s make sure we’re ready. That way‚ we can enjoy ourselves to the fullest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.3666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4233.3333332999955,
          "startTime": 84.6
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4233.3333332999955,
          "startTime": 84.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あら、随分気合い入っているみたいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My‚ you seem quite fired up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 88.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私からの激励は、いらなかったかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess you won’t be needing a pep talk from me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "姫野さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ms. Himeno…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "盗み聞きですか？　随分とまあ、悪趣味やなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eavesdropping‚ huh? Well‚ that’s very rude.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そういうんじゃないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "初戦があのリズノワとだから、ちょっと心配してたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was just a little worried since your first match is against LizNoir.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "今の星見プロ……いえ、今大会の中でも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right now‚ they’re one of the best in Hoshimi Productions…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "リズノワは指折りの実力者",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ in this entire competition.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もちろん、貴方達やリズノワを負かしたことのある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not underestimating Sunny Peace and Moon Tempest‚ of course.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "サニピや月ストを、侮っている訳ではないけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After all‚ they’ve beaten both you and LizNoir‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "積んできた経験の差を考えれば、リズノワの方が\n頭一つ抜きん出ているから、ですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re saying that because LizNoir is head and shoulders\nabove the rest in terms of experience‚ aren’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そう。だからこそ、ここで確実に潰しておくべきなの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right. That’s why we must ensure we crush them here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "必ず勝ちなさい。いいわね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Make sure you win. Understood?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もちろん、勝ち上がった暁には",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ once you beat them‚",
        "id": ""
      },
